    <ingredient>1/2 cup soy milk</ingredient>
    <ingredient>1 or 1/2 banana (depends on size)</ingredient>
    <ingredient>1 handful frozen blue berries </ingredient>
    <ingredient>1 handful frozen strawberries </ingredient>
    <ingredient>1 TBsp ground linseeds</ingredient>
    <ingredient>1 TBsp chia seeds</ingredient>
    <ingredient>1 TBsp flaxseed oil (organic)</ingredient>
    <ingredient>1 TBsp whey powder (omit if vegan)</ingredient>
    <ingredient>1 handful baby spinach* (optional)</ingredient>

